      <title>美国比特币 ETF 流入量创历史新高，代币流入量接近历史最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-get-third-highest-inflow-with-token-near-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们对美国大选结果的猜测不断升温的背景下，比特币价格接近历史新高，投资于比特币的美国交易所交易基金净流入 8.7 亿美元，为该基金单日流入量第三高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-get-third-highest-inflow-with-token-near-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
